                                    "key" : {"type" : 22, "value" : "NodeContext"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : 23, "value" : "Grim. Karlach has just had her revenge on Gortash, who's responsible for the fact that she's going to die soon. Karlach flew into a helpless rage afterwards, realising she can't be cured. She then left for camp to be alone. Jaheira is not pretending to have any answers here - it's stupid and unfair, we can't do anything to stop it, but we should at least do whatever we can."}
